### ======================================================
### BABYSITE API - TESTES COMPLETOS (REST Client)
### Como usar: Clique em "Send Request" acima de cada bloco
### ======================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### ======================================================
### 1️⃣ CRIAR (CREATE) - POST
### ======================================================

### 1.1 CREATE - Cadastrar Novo Usuário Base
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario_codigo": "USR001",
  "cpf": "12345678900",
  "email_1": "joao.silva@email.com",
  "email_2": "joao2@email.com",
  "telefone": "11999999999",
  "nome": "João Silva"
}

### 1.2 CREATE - Cadastrar Babá (Primeira Babá)
POST {{baseUrl}}/babas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Ana Paula Souza",
  "cpf": "98765432100",
  "telefone": "11988888888",
  "email_1": "anapaula@email.com",
  "email_2": "ana.reserva@email.com",
  "status_cadastro": "Ativa",
  "foto": "foto_ana.jpg",
  "antecedentes_pdf": "antecedentes_ana.pdf"
}

### 1.3 CREATE - Cadastrar Segunda Babá
POST {{baseUrl}}/babas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Beatriz Oliveira",
  "cpf": "11122233344",
  "telefone": "21987654321",
  "email_1": "beatriz.oliva@email.com",
  "status_cadastro": "Ativa",
  "foto": "foto_beatriz.jpg"
}

